%E6%8A%97%E9%AB%942%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA</a><br />\n華盛頓州現「新冠病毒派對」 ，刻意染病冀獲抗體，2人確診<br />\n<br />\n美國新冠肺炎疫情嚴重，惟重災區之一的華盛頓州竟出現「新冠病毒派對」，故意讓人接觸確診患者，試圖透過感染病毒獲得抗體，至今最少2人確診。<br />\n<br />\n華盛頓州東南部沃拉沃拉縣當地周二（5日）有94人確診，包括一個肉類加工廠感染群組，衞生官員調查當地部分確診個案時，發現與「新冠病毒派對」有關，本周更有1個或以上的派對，至少2人確診，官員說：「我們詢問其接觸史，發現有25人當時正參加病毒派對。」"},{"pid":"89dc0c22eebd772b89187bb43b069d4f67491147","tid":2077642,"uid":65194,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"efe8b69b45f81a9f2f6b8c62beb3d092c9f19094","tid":2077642,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:19:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4444670\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120944%2F4444670&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=135cc26a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4444670</a><br />\n<br />\n美國年輕人舉辦「新冠肺炎派對」 <br />\n已有1人確診<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2636851/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E8%8F%AF%E7%9B%9B%E9%A0%93%E5%B7%9E%E7%8F%BE%E3%80%8C%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%B4%BE%E5%B0%8D%E3%80%8D%20%E5%88%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85%E5%86%80%E7%8D%B2%E6%8A%97%E9%AB%942%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2636851%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%259B%259B%25E9%25A0%2593%25E5%25B7%259E%25E7%258F%25BE%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25B0%258D%25E3%2580%258D%2520%25E5%2588%25BB%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%2586%2580%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%258A%2597%25E9%25AB%25942%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=b5dce6a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2636851/%E3%80%90%E6%9